Missing in implementation
=========================

In version 2.2 a number of bifrost features are not
yet implemented for all platforms.
The following is a list of the ramaining parts:

      AbstractGraphicalObject.InteractiveScale
      AbstractGraphicalObject.InteractiveRotate
      PictureShape.GetControls
      Picture.InteractiveCreateShape
      Picture.InteractiveReshape
      Picture.InteractiveCombineShape
      Bitmap.WriteToPBMfile
      IntegerList
      GrayMap
      Shape.Insert
      Shape.Delete
      Shape.AppendShape
      Shape.ConnectShape
      Shape.ConnectShapeSmooth
      Line.dashes
      MultiLine.dashes
      PixMap.WriteToPPMfile
      PixMap.ReadFromPPMfile
      Picture.DrawOnPixmap
      TiledSolidColor.writePS
      RasterPaint.writePS
      WinNT: 
      	BitMap.ReadFromPBMfile
	TiledSolidColor
        Canvas.MMtoPixels
        Canvas.PixelsToMM
      Macintosh:
	The current version of Bifrost is not available for Macintosh.

Problems with demos
===================

As a consequence of the WinNT specific limitations mentioned above, the
following demos does not work correctly on Windows NT and Windows 95:

Caused by missing Bitmap.ReadFromPBMfile implementation:
-------------------------------------------------------
background
halloween
menusubway
palettesubway
subway
Tiling

Caused by missing TiledSolidColor implementation:
------------------------------------------------
halftones

Caused by missing RasterPaint implementation:
--------------------------------------------
rasterpaint

Caused by missing Canvas.MMtoPixels implementation:
--------------------------------------------------
frontpage

Caused by shortcomings in Graphictext implementation:
----------------------------------------------------
hatching
loadpicture
storepicture
textedit

Problems with bdraw
===================

Currently unimplemented:
      Undo
      Ungroup
      Smooth
      Unsmooth 
      ReverseOrientation 
      Move
      Move To
      Scale
      Rotate
      Flip Horizontal
      Flip Vertical
      Zoom  
      Some dialogs are not yet implemented for Lidskjalv

Buggy:
      Cut, Clear, Delete
      Group, ungroup 

WinNT: 
      Native (non-postscript) print does not work.
